# Target modern browsers to reduce polyfills and bundle size
# This eliminates legacy JavaScript transforms mentioned in Lighthouse

# Modern browsers with good market share
>0.2%
not dead
not op_mini all

# Support last 2 versions of major browsers
last 2 Chrome versions
last 2 Firefox versions
last 2 Safari versions
last 2 Edge versions

# Exclude older browsers that require heavy polyfills
not IE 11
not IE_Mob 11
not Android < 5
not Samsung < 10
